<br>
While I definitely want HL2, I suspect the release may be pushed back (though I don't want it to be).<br>
<br>
There's also Deus Ex 2 and UT2004 to look forward to (and before anyone complains about 2k3, it's a fine game, it's just not UT with prettier graphics, sorry). Also Halo PC and possibly Far Cry (looks decent...).<br>
<br>
I think we'll see some very nice mods to HL2, given the amount of work that Valve seems to be doing to make it as easy as possible. I'll definitely pick that one up first since I'm keen on the single player game. I haven't been playing many multiplayer games online lately anyway...tend to binge on those at LAN parties <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shousetsu>Shousetsu</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.newelysium.com/forum/psicon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 1:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=746.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.newelysium.com/forum/unclejesse.jpg width=100 height=84></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: this month?</span><hr size=1> farcry looks to be the best multiplayer game that will be available. CS:CZ is going to suck I think since its based off the same old engine (probably why its called condition zero and not a true sequel), which means regular CS but with new maps and weapons. It looked cool 2 years ago but now I have a feeling its going to be just plain lame since they are 2 years too late in releasing it.<br>
<br>
HL2 still has a sept 30th release date, that was confirmed by Valve just a few days ago. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.newelysium.com"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.newelysium.com/forum/banner.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=agentcryrid>Agent Cryrid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 2:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=746.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://sc.groups.msn.com/tn/E6/91/SaiyajinsBloodRPG/1/1.jpg height=96 width=83></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: this month?</span><hr size=1> I'd love to get HL2, but I know for a fact my computer could not handle it.  <p>-- I have no signature. . </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=madpower1>Madpower1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 3:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=746.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/arialraver/Ezboard.txt height=60 width=130></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: this month?</span><hr size=1> CS may not have top of the line graphics but I still perfer game play over graphics anyday. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.madpowermovies.cjb.net/"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/arialraver/ezboardbanner.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> * Newest combo vid- MvC2 exbo</p><i>Edi