sium.com/forum/banner.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=madpower1>Madpower1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 6:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=746.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/arialraver/Ezboard.txt height=60 width=130></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: this month?</span><hr size=1> I hear you. I hope the gameplay isn't EXACTLY the same, if it it then i will be kind of a disapointment. I'll still check it out though.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.madpowermovies.cjb.net/"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/arialraver/ezboardbanner.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> * Newest combo vid- MvC2 exbo</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rageunleashed001>RageUnleashed001</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 6:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=746.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.rage-unleashed.biz/images/grahf.jpg height=100 width=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: this month?</span><hr size=1> Half Life 2 is gonna be awesome. Anyone download the 30 minute 300+ meg E3 footage. Utterly amazing. <br>
