at CS is a bit old, and possibly overratted, but I think it's a lot more fun than the jump and gun games out there.<br>
<br>
I like CS's realistic guns, and the fact that it penalizes for death instead of just spamming the attack button just so that you'll respawn faster.<br>
<br>
